Russia May Revise Tobacco, Alcohol Tax Quarterly, Vedomosti Says

-- B y   Y u l i y a   F e d o r i n o v a
-- 
2011-10-06T05:07:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-06/russia-may-revise-tobacco-alcohol-tax-quarterly-vedomosti-says.html
Russia may revise alcohol and tobacco
taxes every quarter, starting in 2013,  Vedomosti  reported today,
citing Sergei Shatalov, the deputy finance minister. At present,
the taxes are revised once a year, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Yuliya Fedorinova in Moscow at 
 yfedorinova@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Viljoen at 
 jviljoen@bloomberg.net  